# Android Emulator Manager (AEM)

## Project Overview

Build a production-quality Flutter Windows desktop application named **Android Emulator Manager (AEM)**.

The application should help Android developers manage Android Studio emulators quickly without opening Android Studio.

The application should live in the Windows System Tray, automatically detect installed Android SDKs and AVDs, launch emulators, monitor running status, pin favorite devices, and provide a modern Material 3 interface.

This project must follow Clean Architecture, SOLID principles, and production-quality Flutter code.

The final result should be suitable for open-source release and commercial use.

